WEBVTT

01:38.030 --> 01:41.039
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.050 --> 01:43.940
[Episode 6]

01:46.039 --> 01:47.430
Alright, let's eat.

01:47.430 --> 01:48.490
Come on, let's eat.

01:50.710 --> 01:52.920
Hurry up and get the duty staff
from the executive floor.

01:52.920 --> 01:53.560
Now!

01:54.789 --> 01:55.560
Come on.

01:56.000 --> 01:57.789
Eat more.

01:58.150 --> 02:00.640
The baby needs to eat more too.

02:08.630 --> 02:09.310
Come on.

02:09.310 --> 02:10.590
Let's have a drink.

02:10.590 --> 02:11.120
Okay.

02:17.710 --> 02:18.430
Miyu.

02:20.360 --> 02:21.630
I've been looking for you.

02:21.630 --> 02:23.000
What is it, Ms. Zhang?

02:23.070 --> 02:24.520
Private room 808 in the Chinese restaurant

02:24.520 --> 02:25.280
needs a hand.

02:25.280 --> 02:26.280
Can you head over?

02:28.310 --> 02:29.710
But I'm already off work.

02:29.750 --> 02:30.840
I know.

02:31.180 --> 02:33.000
But the others are busy
and can't get away.

02:33.000 --> 02:33.750
Do me a favor.

02:34.360 --> 02:35.620
I'll pay you overtime.

02:38.150 --> 02:38.750
Alright.

02:39.000 --> 02:40.430
I'll tidy up and go over.

02:46.630 --> 02:50.030
[Happy Birthday to Dear Mom]

02:46.690 --> 02:47.430
Come on, Mom.

02:48.280 --> 02:49.280
Cheers to you.

02:49.400 --> 02:51.680
Happy 60th birthday.

02:51.680 --> 02:52.400
May your fortune be as vast
as the East Sea,

02:52.400 --> 02:53.750
and your life as long
as the Southern Mountains.

02:53.750 --> 02:54.280
-My son.
-Wait.

02:54.280 --> 02:55.079
What's wrong?

02:55.280 --> 02:56.680
Mom should be 16,

02:56.680 --> 02:57.840
not 60.

02:57.840 --> 02:58.770
You're so sweet.

03:00.460 --> 03:01.840
Your daughter-in-law

03:01.840 --> 03:03.560
is such a sweet talker.

03:05.000 --> 03:05.750
Thanks to her,

03:05.750 --> 03:08.110
the grandson
we've been waiting for for years

03:08.110 --> 03:09.380
is finally on the way.

03:08.770 --> 03:10.880
[Happy Birthday to Dear Mom]

03:10.280 --> 03:12.000
I'm so pleased.

03:12.140 --> 03:12.560
Mom,

03:12.560 --> 03:14.690
how do you know it's a boy?

03:15.680 --> 03:17.190
You're in great condition,

03:17.190 --> 03:18.280
even like a sister to me.

03:18.280 --> 03:18.680
Hello.

03:18.680 --> 03:20.190
How can I help you?

03:24.400 --> 03:25.560
Isn't this Miyu?

03:29.190 --> 03:30.470
Sorry, I got the wrong room.

03:30.470 --> 03:31.470
Stop right there!

03:31.910 --> 03:33.040
Why are you running?

03:33.390 --> 03:34.470
You took forever to get here.

03:34.470 --> 03:36.110
Hurry up and come in to clean up.

03:36.110 --> 03:36.910
Hurry!

03:40.190 --> 03:41.000
Mr. Feng,

03:41.000 --> 03:42.400
there's something else
in the HSKP Department.

03:42.400 --> 03:43.310
How about I call...

03:43.310 --> 03:44.000
No, you-

03:44.000 --> 03:44.630
If she's busy,

03:44.630 --> 03:45.560
let her go.

03:45.560 --> 03:46.820
Just get someone else.

03:49.420 --> 03:51.280
Follow Mr. Feng's instructions.

03:51.630 --> 03:53.070
Mrs. Nie is right.

03:53.100 --> 03:54.750
Hurry up and clean in here.

03:55.270 --> 03:57.200
Whatever it is, deal with it later.

03:57.310 --> 04:00.170
Change the bone dishes
in front of the guests first.

04:00.680 --> 04:01.680
Now!

04:13.430 --> 04:14.390
How's the food?

04:17.870 --> 04:18.600
Come on.

04:18.600 --> 04:19.390
Eat.

04:20.680 --> 04:21.600
How is it?

04:21.600 --> 04:22.560
Mom, sit closer to me.

04:22.560 --> 04:24.220
Don't get your clothes dirty.

04:33.830 --> 04:35.430
Are you done eating?

04:43.830 --> 04:44.680
Thanks.

04:45.670 --> 04:46.930
Please pick it up.

05:28.280 --> 05:28.920
Mom.

05:30.490 --> 05:31.550
What are you doing?

05:32.110 --> 05:34.000
Sorry, Mom. I didn't mean it.

05:34.130 --> 05:35.520
What's wrong with you?

05:35.890 --> 05:37.690
You made the floor so slippery!

05:37.720 --> 05:39.430
I almost fell!

05:39.600 --> 05:41.280
Yeah. Did you hear that?

05:41.310 --> 05:42.280
How do you work?

05:42.300 --> 05:44.090
Aren't you going
to hurry over and wipe it clean?

05:44.090 --> 05:45.130
Apologize to the guests.

05:44.290 --> 05:46.230
[Happy Birthday to Dear Mom]

05:45.159 --> 05:45.830
Do you even want to work here?

05:45.830 --> 05:46.510
Go now!

05:55.240 --> 05:58.159
Why are you using a dirty towel
to wipe my mom's clothes?

05:58.159 --> 05:59.060
Mr. Feng.

05:59.360 --> 06:00.270
What's wrong with you?

06:00.270 --> 06:01.240
Are your hotel attendants

06:01.240 --> 06:02.480
all so careless?

06:03.980 --> 06:04.980
What's your name?

06:05.480 --> 06:06.680
Do you still want to work here?

06:06.680 --> 06:07.940
-Alright.
-Forget it.

06:08.000 --> 06:08.800
Listen to me,

06:09.600 --> 06:11.240
I didn't even hire this attendant.

06:11.240 --> 06:12.040
I, Feng Kaixin,

06:12.040 --> 06:13.720
would never hire such a person

06:13.800 --> 06:14.800
into our Purong Hotel.

06:14.800 --> 06:15.600
I know.

06:15.600 --> 06:16.560
Didn't you say it?

06:16.560 --> 06:17.800
She's from the HSKP Department.

06:17.800 --> 06:19.160
It's normal that
she doesn't know how to do it.

06:19.160 --> 06:20.420
Just get someone else.

06:21.920 --> 06:22.920
You heard it.

06:23.300 --> 06:24.100
You're lucky

06:24.130 --> 06:25.550
the guest didn't hold you accountable.

06:25.550 --> 06:26.470
Get out of here!

06:42.040 --> 06:42.920
Have you forgotten

06:42.890 --> 06:44.700
♪ A flicker of dim light ♪

06:42.920 --> 06:44.950
about helping my ex-husband
lie to me last time

06:44.950 --> 06:45.950
so quickly?

06:46.240 --> 06:47.240
Thanks to you,

06:46.400 --> 06:48.280
♪ A bowl of warm soup ♪

06:47.850 --> 06:49.409
I'm not Mrs. Nie anymore.

06:50.260 --> 06:52.260
♪ People in the city ♪

06:50.920 --> 06:52.360
You just let her go like that?

06:52.360 --> 06:53.390
Alright.

06:52.990 --> 06:56.030
♪ Squeezing into the hustle and bustle ♪

06:53.390 --> 06:54.920
Could you at least say less?

06:54.930 --> 06:56.130
It's Mom's birthday.

06:56.600 --> 06:57.810
Don't be angry.

06:57.860 --> 06:59.580
♪ The palms of time ♪

07:01.580 --> 07:04.720
♪ Grinding away the simple days ♪

07:05.340 --> 07:08.260
♪ Sprinkling them into this busy world ♪

07:09.260 --> 07:11.300
♪ To be tasted, bit by bit ♪

07:12.780 --> 07:15.980
♪ Embracing this radiant world ♪

07:16.570 --> 07:19.600
♪ Keeps the heart from fading to grey ♪

07:20.190 --> 07:23.310
♪ Life's joy, sorrow, cold, and warmth ♪

07:20.360 --> 07:22.060
-Sorry.
-It's okay.

07:22.240 --> 07:22.920
Come on.

07:23.270 --> 07:24.040
Why bother?

07:24.040 --> 07:25.240
Don't get upset.

07:24.050 --> 07:26.530
♪ Intertwined within the mundane ♪

07:25.240 --> 07:26.570
It's my mom's birthday.

07:26.720 --> 07:27.480
Come on, sit.

07:28.090 --> 07:31.400
♪ Let us bravely gather up ♪

07:28.550 --> 07:29.560
I'll go to the restroom.

07:29.560 --> 07:30.240
Help yourselves.

07:30.240 --> 07:30.830
Okay.

07:31.950 --> 07:35.320
♪ The forgotten past ♪

07:33.040 --> 07:33.830
Well,

07:34.270 --> 07:35.550
one mere attendant

07:35.580 --> 07:37.159
messed up the atmosphere for everyone.

07:36.300 --> 07:38.570
♪ There may be regrets ♪

07:37.720 --> 07:38.800
I'll fine myself with a drink.

07:38.800 --> 07:39.680
Bottoms up.

07:40.230 --> 07:42.470
♪ There may be loneliness ♪

07:41.040 --> 07:42.360
Okay, stop rushing me.

07:42.360 --> 07:43.270
I got the food.

07:43.270 --> 07:43.920
Five minutes.

07:43.920 --> 07:44.820
Three minutes, okay?

07:44.820 --> 07:45.620
I promise-

07:50.159 --> 07:51.820
About what happened just now.

07:53.360 --> 07:54.120
I'm sorry.

07:54.600 --> 07:56.130
I didn't know you were here.

07:58.480 --> 08:00.360
You care so much about other women.

08:00.360 --> 08:01.620
Won't your wife get mad?

08:01.620 --> 08:02.820
I don't care all that.

08:03.040 --> 08:04.120
Seeing you like this

08:04.120 --> 08:04.920
makes me

08:05.270 --> 08:06.480
feel terrible.

08:06.580 --> 08:08.160
If you need help,

08:08.360 --> 08:09.240
I'll help you.

08:09.270 --> 08:11.200
What's wrong with me like this now?

08:12.120 --> 08:14.180
I make my own money to support myself.

08:14.800 --> 08:17.930
Is it any more shameful
than being your full-time nanny?

08:18.920 --> 08:21.040
You don't have to speak so coldly.

08:21.480 --> 08:23.360
Yes. I admit it—we did get divorced.

08:23.360 --> 08:24.240
But to me,

08:24.240 --> 08:25.770
you've always been family.

08:27.480 --> 08:29.240
And I still have some

08:29.240 --> 08:30.920
connections or resources

08:30.920 --> 08:31.680
in hotel marketing.

08:31.680 --> 08:32.270
If you need them,

08:32.270 --> 08:33.000
I can help you.

08:33.000 --> 08:34.539
That's enough, Nie Yucheng.

08:34.539 --> 08:35.840
I appreciate your kindness,

08:35.840 --> 08:37.230
but I don't need anything.

08:37.230 --> 08:38.240
If there's nothing else,

08:38.240 --> 08:39.000
I'm leaving.

08:39.720 --> 08:41.850
Wait, I haven't finished. Can we talk?

08:43.150 --> 08:45.270
What are you two doing?

08:45.840 --> 08:47.390
What are you afraid of?

08:48.390 --> 08:49.550
Miyu. Miyu!

08:50.270 --> 08:51.400
Where are you going?

08:54.670 --> 08:55.650
Honey.

08:57.240 --> 08:58.720
You went to the bathroom for so long.

08:58.720 --> 09:00.270
Isn't there one in the private room?

09:00.270 --> 09:01.790
I have some things to discuss with her.

09:01.790 --> 09:03.550
I have nothing to discuss with you.

09:03.550 --> 09:05.270
Please take him away immediately.

09:05.270 --> 09:06.120
Xu Miyu,

09:06.430 --> 09:08.360
you and Nie Yucheng are in the past.

09:08.550 --> 09:10.240
Can't you just part ways peacefully?

09:10.240 --> 09:12.600
Stop pestering my husband like this.

09:12.910 --> 09:14.270
This is already seriously

09:14.270 --> 09:15.470
affecting our lives.

09:15.910 --> 09:17.120
Me pestering him?

09:17.270 --> 09:18.720
Why don't you ask your husband himself

09:18.720 --> 09:20.150
why he cornered me here

09:20.150 --> 09:22.150
and what disgusting things he said to me?

09:22.150 --> 09:23.790
Instead of wasting time messing with me,

09:23.790 --> 09:25.790
you should keep your own man in line.

09:27.840 --> 09:29.500
Alright, stop making a scene.

09:30.720 --> 09:31.910
Look at her attitude.

09:31.910 --> 09:33.570
What kind of attitude is that?

09:34.150 --> 09:34.770
Mr. Nie,

09:34.840 --> 09:35.630
Mrs. Nie.

09:36.840 --> 09:38.510
Everyone in the room is looking for you.

09:38.510 --> 09:39.030
Okay.

09:39.270 --> 09:40.070
Let's go back.

09:41.040 --> 09:41.890
Alright.

09:42.720 --> 09:43.550
Alright.

09:57.860 --> 09:58.590
Miyu.

09:57.890 --> 10:00.040
[Dad]

09:59.120 --> 10:01.030
What has your husband
been busy with lately?

10:01.030 --> 10:02.350
Why isn't he answering the phone?

10:02.000 --> 10:03.120
[Dad]

10:07.890 --> 10:09.220
Why are you calling him?

10:10.560 --> 10:13.710
[Dad]

10:12.720 --> 10:15.650
To ask him to bring
more customers to the guesthouse.

10:17.110 --> 10:21.400
[Dad]

10:20.720 --> 10:22.050
Don't call him anymore.

10:23.440 --> 10:28.140
[Dad Inviting You to Voice Chat]

10:34.150 --> 10:34.910
Look,

10:35.760 --> 10:37.360
she's getting more and more outrageous.

10:37.360 --> 10:39.160
Not answering my calls anymore.

10:42.180 --> 10:44.220
And she told me not to call Yucheng.

10:45.680 --> 10:47.200
Do you think I want to call him?

10:47.200 --> 10:49.240
If there were any other good way,

10:49.290 --> 10:51.020
would I need to beg her husband?

10:51.720 --> 10:55.080
Are they still having conflicts?

10:55.600 --> 10:58.480
Why do I feel like
Miyu has been acting weird lately?

10:59.130 --> 11:01.000
She hasn't mentioned Nie Yucheng at all.

11:01.000 --> 11:02.480
How big of a conflict

11:03.000 --> 11:04.440
can those two have living together?

11:04.440 --> 11:05.000
Besides,

11:05.310 --> 11:07.580
even if Yucheng did something wrong,

11:07.630 --> 11:09.360
a few words and it'd be over, right?

11:09.360 --> 11:11.290
They don't have to make a big scene.

11:11.630 --> 11:13.170
I'm just worried she's too

11:13.190 --> 11:15.320
stubborn and doesn't get it.

11:17.170 --> 11:18.170
Then how about...

11:19.840 --> 11:21.510
How about we go check on them?

11:31.910 --> 11:32.580
Mom,

11:33.530 --> 11:35.010
let me drive you home.

11:35.040 --> 11:37.020
Zhenzhen has been busy all night

11:37.040 --> 11:38.370
and isn't feeling well.

11:39.320 --> 11:41.180
Should we take her to the hospital?

11:41.180 --> 11:42.200
Don't let it harm the baby.

11:42.200 --> 11:42.840
No need.

11:42.840 --> 11:43.600
She's just tired.

11:43.600 --> 11:44.460
She'll be fine.

11:46.750 --> 11:47.600
Yucheng,

11:48.120 --> 11:49.840
I must remind you of something.

11:49.840 --> 11:50.620
Go ahead.

11:50.640 --> 11:52.360
Zhenzhen is different from your ex-wife.

11:52.360 --> 11:54.010
She's pregnant
with our Nie family's child.

11:54.010 --> 11:55.600
It's time for you to settle down.

11:55.600 --> 11:57.000
You must never let her down, understand?

11:57.000 --> 11:58.350
Mom, I know.

11:58.600 --> 12:00.000
You can rest assured.

12:00.480 --> 12:01.810
I'm going to be a father.

12:02.000 --> 12:04.480
I'll definitely
live a good life this time.

12:05.080 --> 12:06.120
That's more like it.

12:06.120 --> 12:07.080
Come on, I'll get you home.

12:07.080 --> 12:07.610
Let's go.

12:17.750 --> 12:19.240
When you went to
the Chinese restaurant yesterday,

12:17.780 --> 12:20.420
[Customer Satisfaction Survey]

12:19.240 --> 12:20.720
why did you end up getting a bad review?

12:20.720 --> 12:22.380
I heard the guest was furious,

12:22.480 --> 12:24.360
and complained for over 10 minutes.

12:24.360 --> 12:25.640
They even specifically

12:25.640 --> 12:27.520
marked your name on it.

12:30.750 --> 12:32.610
I heard

12:32.640 --> 12:34.510
you know this guest.

12:36.290 --> 12:37.290
Who told you that?

12:40.070 --> 12:41.190
Anyway,

12:41.240 --> 12:42.940
these kinds of specific complaints

12:42.940 --> 12:44.060
are quite serious.

12:44.480 --> 12:46.810
You need to reflect on your work properly.

12:46.870 --> 12:47.480
Miyu,

12:47.610 --> 12:49.340
that's your second bad review.

12:49.590 --> 12:51.250
You have to take it seriously.

12:55.510 --> 12:58.160
The legal wife
being humiliated by the mistress?

12:58.160 --> 12:59.900
Is it really that dramatic?

13:00.510 --> 13:01.270
Yeah.

13:01.320 --> 13:03.240
And according to the HSKP Department,

13:03.240 --> 13:05.840
she caught them cheating
on the executive floor.

13:05.840 --> 13:06.880
Oh my.

13:07.000 --> 13:09.240
And she's still
working here as an attendant?

13:09.240 --> 13:10.440
Is she a masochist?

13:10.440 --> 13:11.750
She has to make a living.

13:11.750 --> 13:12.360
I heard

13:12.360 --> 13:14.240
she used to act like
she owned this place not long ago,

13:14.240 --> 13:16.150
spending thousands in one night.

13:16.360 --> 13:18.360
What goes around comes around.

13:19.360 --> 13:20.840
Didn't they say her ex-husband

13:20.840 --> 13:22.480
has close ties with Purong?

13:22.710 --> 13:23.450
Maybe

13:23.480 --> 13:25.480
she's playing the victim here on purpose

13:25.480 --> 13:27.880
to find a chance
to win back her ex-husband.

13:34.410 --> 13:35.410
Sorry about that.

13:36.360 --> 13:37.530
What's wrong with her?

13:37.530 --> 13:38.450
That's her.

14:13.320 --> 14:15.600
Did you hear about
that person on the executive floor?

14:15.600 --> 14:16.670
Yeah, I heard.

14:17.480 --> 14:19.750
-So many people are talking about it.
-Divorced and came out to be an attendant.

14:19.750 --> 14:20.510
And then she just happened to run into

14:20.510 --> 14:22.240
her ex-husband's family coming to eat.

14:22.240 --> 14:23.240
It's so mortifying.

14:23.240 --> 14:24.040
Exactly.

14:24.090 --> 14:27.950
-How could she still keep working here?
-I definitely couldn't do it.

14:28.240 --> 14:30.440
Did you hear
she spent a lot of money before?

14:30.440 --> 14:31.720
-Yeah, I heard.
-And ended up here being an attendant.

14:31.720 --> 14:32.360
Exactly.

14:34.000 --> 14:35.870
Our circle is just this samll.

14:38.660 --> 14:40.310
Starting today,

14:40.350 --> 14:41.600
I'll do every thing I want to do,

14:41.600 --> 14:42.690
say every word I want to say.

14:42.690 --> 14:43.960
I won't be watching
for your approval anymore.

14:43.960 --> 14:46.090
I won't care if you're happy or not.

14:46.120 --> 14:48.660
I only care if I'm happy.

14:49.020 --> 14:51.380
I want to go back to 10 years ago,

14:51.410 --> 14:53.360
that turning point that changed my life,

14:53.360 --> 14:55.420
to see if I can realize my value in life

14:55.600 --> 14:57.360
through my own efforts.

14:58.470 --> 15:00.800
No matter how many lofty ambitions I have,

15:01.360 --> 15:03.090
they're ruthlessly shattered

15:04.480 --> 15:06.480
along with my self-esteem

15:07.010 --> 15:08.300
at this moment.

15:10.090 --> 15:11.660
Physical hardships

15:11.760 --> 15:13.110
and mental pressure

15:13.820 --> 15:16.550
are gradually consuming
my hopes for the future,

15:16.970 --> 15:20.220
making me gradually realize a cruel fact.

15:21.230 --> 15:22.630
The me right now

15:23.890 --> 15:26.970
may have already
lost the chance to start over.

15:27.110 --> 15:29.310
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

16:05.140 --> 16:07.150
♪ Life is full of ♪

16:07.930 --> 16:10.620
♪ Countless crossroads ♪

16:08.210 --> 16:17.290
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

16:12.290 --> 16:16.050
♪ Chase joy too hard, and it slips away ♪

16:17.720 --> 16:19.670
♪ All those confusions ♪

16:20.320 --> 16:24.040
♪ No answers, no reasons ♪

16:22.860 --> 16:25.910
Everyone keeps
moving forward without stopping.

16:24.920 --> 16:28.920
♪ Throwing ourselves
into the tide of the unknown ♪

16:26.780 --> 16:28.030
Only me,

16:28.920 --> 16:31.650
getting trapped
in the same spot again and again.

16:32.320 --> 16:34.730
♪ Knowing when to advance or retreat,
yet still asleep ♪

16:32.880 --> 16:34.670
I really want to run away,

16:35.600 --> 16:37.560
but I can't even find

16:35.850 --> 16:37.770
♪ Rushing to ripen before our time ♪

16:37.770 --> 16:40.510
a place for myself in such a big city,

16:39.250 --> 16:43.250
♪ Sighing at partings,
who meets whom at which crossing ♪

16:45.120 --> 16:47.050
♪ Busy and restless ♪

16:47.520 --> 16:50.950
♪ No turning back, no stopping ♪

16:52.270 --> 16:56.440
♪ Our path—do you see it now ♪

16:56.520 --> 16:58.400
Are you running away?

17:05.240 --> 17:07.099
If you think that by giving up now,

17:07.310 --> 17:09.510
all your difficulties will disappear,

17:09.700 --> 17:12.359
then cutting your losses in time
is a good thing.

17:12.440 --> 17:15.300
After all, your personality
is too accommodating.

17:15.310 --> 17:17.200
To do well in the hotel industry,

17:17.500 --> 17:18.760
it's going to be tough.

18:00.940 --> 18:01.740
Hello, Mr. Ji.

18:03.910 --> 18:05.170
Why are you still here?

18:05.200 --> 18:06.200
Working as usual.

18:06.640 --> 18:07.370
Not leaving?

18:07.510 --> 18:08.240
Not leaving.

18:08.640 --> 18:10.350
If I left on my own,

18:10.380 --> 18:13.040
wouldn't that play
right into someone's hands?

18:16.720 --> 18:17.510
Also,

18:18.880 --> 18:20.450
whether I'm suited for this work

18:20.450 --> 18:21.980
is not for others to decide.

18:43.270 --> 18:45.210
Thanks for today, Qin.

18:45.440 --> 18:46.000
Don't mention it.

18:46.000 --> 18:46.510
We're neighbors,

18:46.510 --> 18:47.570
and it's on the way.

18:49.360 --> 18:52.110
Should we call Miyu again?

18:52.840 --> 18:54.510
If she doesn't answer,
she must still be asleep.

18:54.510 --> 18:55.550
Don't call her.

18:57.550 --> 19:00.210
Doesn't your daughter
go to work in the morning?

19:01.030 --> 19:02.400
She never goes to work.

19:02.420 --> 19:05.310
She can sleep as long as she wants.

19:08.790 --> 19:10.240
In their family,

19:10.640 --> 19:12.070
our daughter is in charge,

19:12.070 --> 19:14.320
and the son-in-law
is responsible for making money.

19:14.320 --> 19:16.020
Then your son-in-law is really something.

19:16.020 --> 19:16.640
One person makes money

19:16.640 --> 19:17.970
for two people to spend.

19:18.030 --> 19:19.630
How much does he have to make?

19:20.000 --> 19:21.590
Qin, let me tell you,

19:21.680 --> 19:23.860
how much money he makes
really isn't the main point.

19:23.860 --> 19:25.440
The key is that my son-in-law‘s

19:25.440 --> 19:27.170
biggest merit is that

19:27.190 --> 19:28.390
he's good to his wife.

19:29.580 --> 19:30.630
Yes.

19:31.070 --> 19:32.860
He treats our Miyu

19:32.890 --> 19:34.130
really well.

19:35.030 --> 19:36.760
A harmonious family prospers.

19:36.920 --> 19:37.680
Xu,

19:37.680 --> 19:39.540
you're about to enjoy a good life.

19:50.480 --> 19:51.160
Alright.

19:51.960 --> 19:52.790
Let's talk later.

19:52.790 --> 19:53.340
Okay.

19:53.440 --> 19:53.960
Okay.

19:54.130 --> 19:54.570
Okay.

19:56.190 --> 19:57.200
Okay, take this.

19:58.480 --> 19:59.720
Thank you, Qin.

19:59.720 --> 20:00.550
-Bye.
-Thanks.

20:00.550 --> 20:01.000
Okay.

20:01.000 --> 20:01.570
Bye.

20:01.990 --> 20:03.250
Here, let me take this.

20:18.270 --> 20:20.750
How about we call Miyu again?

20:20.790 --> 20:21.790
We're already at the door.

20:21.790 --> 20:23.000
Why call?

20:23.000 --> 20:23.680
Just enter it.

20:23.680 --> 20:25.160
You know the code.

20:30.070 --> 20:30.720
Come in.

20:31.270 --> 20:32.120
Honey,

20:32.400 --> 20:33.400
did you forget...

20:34.270 --> 20:35.270
Who are you?

20:35.480 --> 20:36.510
How did you get in?

20:36.510 --> 20:37.000
You...

20:37.240 --> 20:38.240
Where's my phone?

20:38.790 --> 20:39.310
Get out.

20:39.750 --> 20:40.270
Get out!

20:40.270 --> 20:41.720
This is my daughter's house.

20:41.720 --> 20:43.640
Why can't we come in?

20:43.640 --> 20:44.160
Right.

20:44.160 --> 20:45.550
I haven't even asked who you are.

20:45.550 --> 20:46.480
It's my daughter's house.

20:46.480 --> 20:47.030
You...

20:56.510 --> 20:58.160
What's she busy with?

20:58.240 --> 20:59.640
Her own house has been...

20:59.720 --> 21:00.920
She's not answering.

21:01.510 --> 21:02.640
Keep calling.

21:04.240 --> 21:05.000
What now?

21:06.240 --> 21:07.510
Have you sorted it out?

21:07.640 --> 21:09.570
Your daughter has been kicked out.

21:10.160 --> 21:12.640
Now I'm the mistress of this house.

21:12.940 --> 21:13.330
[Marriage Certificate]

21:22.060 --> 21:23.070
You slut!

21:23.070 --> 21:23.640
You...

21:23.790 --> 21:24.650
Don't you dare!

21:24.750 --> 21:25.960
If you dare do anything,

21:25.960 --> 21:27.620
I'll sue you for trespassing.

21:30.720 --> 21:31.400
Well,

21:32.510 --> 21:34.030
Lu Zhenzhen.

21:34.920 --> 21:35.480
Look,

21:35.790 --> 21:36.720
it's not easy

21:36.720 --> 21:38.580
for us to come all this way.

21:38.720 --> 21:39.440
This is

21:39.440 --> 21:40.680
the only home we have in Shanghai.

21:40.680 --> 21:42.400
If we don't see our daughter

21:42.400 --> 21:43.730
and clear this up today,

21:43.880 --> 21:45.050
we won't leave.

21:45.560 --> 21:46.190
Right.

21:46.270 --> 21:47.160
We won't leave.

21:50.790 --> 21:52.450
You want to see your daughter?

21:53.080 --> 21:53.880
Alright.

21:53.910 --> 21:55.040
I'll give you a ride.

21:58.480 --> 21:59.200
Okay.

22:08.920 --> 22:09.960
Your daughter is in there.

22:09.960 --> 22:11.200
Go find her yourself.

22:27.620 --> 22:30.090
How did that slut know Miyu lived here?

22:30.410 --> 22:32.510
What's the relationship between them?

22:32.510 --> 22:33.920
Could she be tricking us?

22:43.180 --> 22:44.560
I just forgot to ask.

22:44.620 --> 22:46.860
Which room does Miyu live in?

22:47.030 --> 22:49.690
How long will it take
to check every single room?

22:52.310 --> 22:53.200
Let's go ask.

23:00.480 --> 23:01.550
Excuse me.

23:01.720 --> 23:02.510
Mom.

23:03.070 --> 23:03.920
Miyu!

23:05.560 --> 23:06.360
Dad.

23:07.240 --> 23:07.720
Miyu.

23:07.720 --> 23:08.680
What are you doing here?

23:08.680 --> 23:09.200
You...

23:09.640 --> 23:10.480
How...

23:10.910 --> 23:11.660
How come...

23:12.270 --> 23:13.270
Come in.

23:17.480 --> 23:18.800
Black Card Ji's room.

23:19.790 --> 23:21.530
Why are you dressed like this?

23:22.030 --> 23:24.200
W-Why aren't you staying at home?

23:24.240 --> 23:25.480
What are you doing here?

23:25.480 --> 23:26.310
I was planning to

23:26.310 --> 23:28.070
tell you about this later.

23:28.070 --> 23:29.200
Tell us what?

23:29.200 --> 23:31.580
There are wedding photos
up on the wall.

23:31.720 --> 23:33.720
Even if I want
to pull that slut's hair,

23:33.720 --> 23:35.480
the police wouldn't help me.

23:35.790 --> 23:36.830
Xu Miyu.

23:36.860 --> 23:38.440
Room 1809 is calling.

23:38.750 --> 23:39.550
Okay, got it.

23:40.270 --> 23:41.680
What are you doing?

23:41.720 --> 23:43.160
Hurry up and come home with me.

23:43.160 --> 23:44.240
We will stand up for you.

23:44.240 --> 23:46.070
We're taking this home back right now.

23:46.070 --> 23:46.480
Mom.

23:46.480 --> 23:48.310
-That's not my home anymore!
-Let's go.

23:48.310 --> 23:49.030
Not your home?

23:49.030 --> 23:50.480
Whose home is it then?

23:53.210 --> 23:53.860
What's going on?

23:53.860 --> 23:54.510
Mr. Ji.

23:55.110 --> 23:56.330
My parents came to see me.

23:56.330 --> 23:57.750
I'll let them leave first.

23:57.750 --> 23:58.680
Let's go.

23:58.680 --> 23:59.440
Go now.

24:00.090 --> 24:01.330
Go.

24:02.510 --> 24:03.310
I'm sorry.

24:03.310 --> 24:04.200
Wait a minute.

24:05.750 --> 24:07.970
Don't bring personal matters to work.

24:08.070 --> 24:09.030
Take the meal coupon.

24:08.270 --> 24:09.150
[Executive Lounge Meal Coupon]

24:10.750 --> 24:11.610
What about you?

24:11.750 --> 24:12.880
I've already eaten.

24:12.910 --> 24:13.630
Thank you.

24:13.350 --> 24:13.700
[Executive Lounge Meal Coupon]

24:14.790 --> 24:15.750
Let's go.

24:15.750 --> 24:16.690
Let's go.

24:24.440 --> 24:25.240
Here.

24:26.480 --> 24:27.510
Here, have some.

24:27.640 --> 24:28.200
Here.

24:29.000 --> 24:29.600
Take this.

24:31.680 --> 24:33.880
Did Nie Yucheng cheat on you?

24:34.270 --> 24:37.270
He cheated and still
has the nerve to bring up divorce?

24:37.550 --> 24:39.480
I'm the one who wanted the divorce.

24:40.790 --> 24:41.880
Have you lost your mind?

24:41.880 --> 24:42.550
Miyu.

24:42.750 --> 24:43.440
Xiumei.

24:43.880 --> 24:44.720
Keep it down.

24:45.160 --> 24:46.480
Mind your image.

24:48.550 --> 24:49.680
You're his wife.

24:49.680 --> 24:50.680
He cheated on you.

24:50.700 --> 24:52.510
Why did you ask for a divorce?

24:52.960 --> 24:54.030
You married him first.

24:54.030 --> 24:55.920
Why would you give in to that slut?

24:55.920 --> 24:56.440
Mom,

24:56.440 --> 24:58.480
this isn't about who came first.

25:02.000 --> 25:03.720
Is that slut pregnant?

25:05.880 --> 25:07.210
Seriously, look at you.

25:07.210 --> 25:08.640
Look at the mess you've made.

25:08.640 --> 25:10.240
Our divorce has nothing to do

25:10.280 --> 25:11.130
with children

25:11.160 --> 25:12.450
or the other woman.

25:12.960 --> 25:15.760
I don't have any feelings
for Nie Yucheng anymore.

25:15.790 --> 25:17.270
I can't go on living like this.

25:17.270 --> 25:18.400
Miyu,

25:19.100 --> 25:21.780
everything in the world
needs to be managed.

25:22.720 --> 25:24.350
It's like growing crops.

25:24.710 --> 25:27.770
When it comes to drought or flood,
you have to find a way.

25:28.040 --> 25:29.410
Don't be penny-wise

25:29.440 --> 25:30.960
and pound-foolish.

25:31.880 --> 25:32.590
Of course,

25:32.940 --> 25:35.000
if you're determined to get a divorce

25:35.000 --> 25:36.370
and never look back,

25:36.400 --> 25:37.330
that's fine too.

25:37.830 --> 25:39.160
Mom and Dad support you.

25:39.680 --> 25:40.880
Let's have a good talk.

25:40.880 --> 25:43.240
How do you plan
to support yourself after the divorce?

25:43.240 --> 25:45.160
I divided the marital property with him.

25:45.160 --> 25:45.530
Right.

25:45.530 --> 25:47.090
So how was it divided?

25:48.250 --> 25:49.370
We have agreed.

25:50.180 --> 25:52.110
Half of the money goes to each of us.

25:52.720 --> 25:55.000
His parents
bought the house before we got married,

25:55.000 --> 25:56.000
so I don't want it.

25:56.280 --> 25:57.360
I don't know how to drive,

25:57.360 --> 25:58.200
so the car is useless to me.

25:58.200 --> 25:58.920
Then,

25:59.080 --> 26:01.380
doesn't it mean
you gave everything to him?

26:01.380 --> 26:04.770
You've taken a huge loss
in the past 10 years.

26:04.800 --> 26:05.610
Stop for now.

26:05.630 --> 26:07.060
Let me talk to her.

26:08.640 --> 26:09.270
Okay.

26:09.510 --> 26:10.310
So,

26:10.310 --> 26:12.200
the house and the car go to him.

26:12.920 --> 26:14.120
What about the money?

26:14.590 --> 26:16.350
How much money did you get?

26:16.680 --> 26:19.590
Nie Yucheng earns millions a year, right?

26:20.550 --> 26:21.310
You should get

26:21.310 --> 26:23.270
at least 8 or 10 million.

26:24.640 --> 26:26.970
Let's invest this money
in the guesthouse

26:27.200 --> 26:28.680
and other businesses too.

26:28.750 --> 26:29.790
Then I think

26:29.790 --> 26:31.310
your life will be secured.

26:31.750 --> 26:33.080
What do you think, Miyu?

26:35.000 --> 26:36.350
He invested the money.

26:37.590 --> 26:38.270
And lost it.

26:40.270 --> 26:41.400
How much did he lose?

26:43.510 --> 26:44.440
He lost it all.

26:44.500 --> 26:45.420
All?

26:47.830 --> 26:48.460
Then...

26:48.550 --> 26:49.680
Then after all this,

26:49.680 --> 26:50.540
doesn't it mean

26:50.750 --> 26:52.270
you didn't get a penny?

26:57.160 --> 26:57.790
Dad,

26:58.590 --> 26:59.200
Mom,

26:59.640 --> 27:01.440
my job is a bit tiring now,

27:01.920 --> 27:04.110
but I earn my own money and spend it.

27:04.590 --> 27:05.960
I feel at ease.

27:08.830 --> 27:11.160
It's just that I might not
be able to pay off

27:11.590 --> 27:13.520
the online loan of 300,000 lately.

27:16.350 --> 27:17.030
What kind of meat is this?

27:17.030 --> 27:17.880
It's so chewy.

27:17.880 --> 27:19.340
Looks good but tastes bad.

27:25.110 --> 27:25.920
Look at you.

27:25.920 --> 27:27.070
Seriously,

27:27.070 --> 27:29.110
why did you mention paying off the debt?

27:29.110 --> 27:29.850
Look.

27:29.940 --> 27:30.720
Miyu.

27:31.030 --> 27:32.030
Room 1826.

27:32.030 --> 27:33.880
The guest wants two more
bottles of mineral water.

27:33.880 --> 27:34.510
Okay.

27:34.510 --> 27:35.200
I'm coming.

27:35.440 --> 27:36.240
Mom,

27:36.400 --> 27:38.350
show Dad around the nearby mall.

27:38.590 --> 27:39.990
I'll find you after work.

27:42.270 --> 27:43.350
Take some food.

27:43.680 --> 27:46.110
Look, you've lost so much weight recently.

27:46.830 --> 27:47.680
I'm going.

27:47.680 --> 27:48.590
Eat it.

27:58.590 --> 27:59.350
Xu!

27:59.590 --> 28:01.040
Where are you going?

28:01.160 --> 28:02.830
Miyu told me to

28:02.830 --> 28:04.510
show you around the mall.

28:04.590 --> 28:05.960
Miyu has suffered so much grievance.

28:05.960 --> 28:07.560
What's there to show around?

28:10.070 --> 28:11.070
Just wait here.

28:11.070 --> 28:12.110
I'm going to take care of something.

28:12.110 --> 28:12.920
You...

28:25.510 --> 28:26.070
Hello.

28:25.790 --> 28:28.820
[Private Customization: Explore Russia]

28:26.510 --> 28:27.030
Miss.

28:27.510 --> 28:29.110
I'm looking for Nie Yucheng.

28:29.590 --> 28:31.250
Have you made an appointment?

28:31.680 --> 28:34.110
Just tell him his father-in-law is here.

28:34.250 --> 28:39.420
[Private Customization: Explore Russia]

28:38.960 --> 28:39.510
Hello?

28:39.640 --> 28:41.710
Someone is at the door
looking for Mr. Nie,

28:41.710 --> 28:43.510
saying he's his father-in-law.

28:43.820 --> 28:44.450
Okay.

28:45.200 --> 28:45.960
I'm sorry.

28:45.960 --> 28:47.420
Mr. Nie is very busy today.

28:49.200 --> 28:49.960
I know.

28:50.180 --> 28:53.070
Mr. Nie is busy every day.

28:53.960 --> 28:54.680
It's fine.

28:54.900 --> 28:55.770
I...

28:55.880 --> 28:56.580
I'll wait for him.

28:56.580 --> 28:57.820
Let him do his things.

29:05.160 --> 29:06.790
You're Nie Yucheng's colleagues, right?

29:06.790 --> 29:08.120
I'm his father-in-law.

29:08.710 --> 29:09.940
I'll just wait for him here.

29:09.940 --> 29:10.590
Go on with your work.

29:10.590 --> 29:11.440
Keqi,

29:11.530 --> 29:12.610
this person refuses to leave.

29:12.610 --> 29:13.560
What should I do?

29:20.110 --> 29:23.990
[Changyang Travel Agency]

29:27.530 --> 29:27.860
Dad.

29:28.200 --> 29:28.880
Yucheng!

29:29.770 --> 29:31.290
What brings you here?

29:31.490 --> 29:32.680
Am I interrupting your work?

29:32.680 --> 29:33.800
No. Come over to the office.

29:33.800 --> 29:34.950
I told them no rush.

29:34.980 --> 29:36.750
Let's talk after you're done with work.

29:36.750 --> 29:38.010
I have plenty of time.

29:38.040 --> 29:39.340
You should have called me.

29:39.340 --> 29:40.540
So I could pick you up.

29:40.700 --> 29:41.620
No need.

29:41.870 --> 29:43.950
We had nothing to do at home anyway.

29:44.590 --> 29:45.320
Well,

29:45.340 --> 29:46.950
our neighbor happened to be driving

29:46.950 --> 29:48.620
to Shanghai for goods,

29:48.650 --> 29:50.780
so your mom and I hitched a ride with him

29:51.370 --> 29:52.500
to come check on you.

29:53.120 --> 29:53.600
Dad,

29:55.640 --> 29:56.440
I'm ashamed.

29:57.720 --> 29:58.950
I've been quite busy lately

29:58.950 --> 30:01.750
and haven't had time
to tell you about many things.

30:02.980 --> 30:04.350
There's no need.

30:04.880 --> 30:06.510
We already know about

30:06.830 --> 30:08.830
what happened between you and Miyu.

30:10.080 --> 30:11.190
I'm sorry, Dad.

30:11.270 --> 30:13.030
This is my fault.

30:15.450 --> 30:17.500
Since you chose to separate,

30:17.740 --> 30:19.800
you must have your own difficulties.

30:20.440 --> 30:21.530
Anyway,

30:21.560 --> 30:22.090
Yucheng,

30:22.560 --> 30:24.560
you were husband and wife after all.

30:24.970 --> 30:26.300
Even if the love is gone,

30:26.300 --> 30:28.360
the gratitude is still there, right?

30:28.840 --> 30:30.840
Look at you, a real social elite,

30:31.460 --> 30:32.700
a successful man

30:33.120 --> 30:34.520
earning millions a year.

30:34.730 --> 30:35.850
Now that you're divorced,

30:35.850 --> 30:38.480
you're being so stingy with your wife.

30:40.030 --> 30:41.800
Doesn't that look bad to you?

30:43.580 --> 30:44.770
Look at you.

30:44.800 --> 30:46.030
Your have a big office

30:46.880 --> 30:48.250
and manage so many people.

30:48.250 --> 30:49.860
You can just offer some money

30:49.890 --> 30:51.490
and make it a decent breakup.

30:52.230 --> 30:53.230
Can't you do that?

30:53.440 --> 30:54.640
Dad, you've misunderstood me.

30:54.640 --> 30:56.510
I really have no money.

30:58.670 --> 30:59.800
When we divorced,

31:00.200 --> 31:01.590
I was deep in debt.

31:02.070 --> 31:03.640
Of course, I made it very clear to Miyu

31:03.640 --> 31:05.710
that she doesn't need to
deal with repaying the debt.

31:05.710 --> 31:06.880
But honestly,

31:06.920 --> 31:08.720
I really don't have any extra money.

31:08.720 --> 31:09.510
Nie Yucheng,

31:10.030 --> 31:11.440
those words of yours

31:11.730 --> 31:13.160
can only fool a child.

31:13.310 --> 31:13.920
What?

31:14.350 --> 31:17.040
You fooled my girl
and now you want to keep fooling me?

31:17.040 --> 31:18.550
Dad, what are you talking about?

31:18.550 --> 31:19.660
How am I fooling you?

31:19.660 --> 31:21.400
Stop pretending with me.

31:22.110 --> 31:22.790
The door is closed,

31:22.790 --> 31:23.510
the curtains are drawn,

31:23.510 --> 31:24.830
and there's nobody else here.

31:24.830 --> 31:25.910
My daughter

31:25.960 --> 31:27.160
has been

31:27.180 --> 31:28.830
with you for so many years.

31:29.250 --> 31:31.650
You have to compensate
for her loss, right?

31:37.920 --> 31:38.720
Fine.

31:40.690 --> 31:42.670
Go ahead.

31:42.920 --> 31:44.740
How do you want me to compensate?

31:47.680 --> 31:48.400
After all,

31:48.400 --> 31:50.030
we used to be family.

31:51.150 --> 31:52.910
Let's settle it by year.

31:53.640 --> 31:54.780
200,000

31:54.870 --> 31:55.600
for one year.

31:56.260 --> 31:57.860
Miyu served you for 10 years.

31:58.060 --> 31:59.520
That's 2 million in total.

31:59.880 --> 32:01.160
You settle this money with me,

32:01.160 --> 32:02.280
and I'll leave immediately.

32:02.280 --> 32:04.280
We will never see each other again.

32:04.710 --> 32:05.510
In the future,

32:05.920 --> 32:07.790
even if you earn
hundreds of millions a year,

32:07.790 --> 32:09.570
it has nothing to do with our family.

32:09.570 --> 32:10.430
What do you say?

32:11.310 --> 32:12.040
To be honest,

32:12.840 --> 32:14.570
this is the first time I've seen

32:14.590 --> 32:17.100
a father selling his daughter
so righteously.

32:17.100 --> 32:18.540
I sell my daughter?

32:18.920 --> 32:21.400
It's not like you're any better.

32:21.430 --> 32:22.670
You were two-timing

32:22.820 --> 32:24.030
and being ungrateful.

32:24.030 --> 32:26.080
You're totally a cheating bastard.

32:26.100 --> 32:26.770
No.

32:26.830 --> 32:27.990
No, well,

32:28.010 --> 32:29.510
you need to be clear about this.

32:29.510 --> 32:30.800
Your daughter and I

32:30.820 --> 32:32.080
are already divorced.

32:32.270 --> 32:33.600
It's in black and white,

32:33.810 --> 32:35.140
nationally certified.

32:35.290 --> 32:36.750
No matter where you sue me,

32:36.780 --> 32:38.820
we have to follow the law, right?

32:40.760 --> 32:41.950
All in all,

32:42.470 --> 32:44.870
you just don't want
to give the money today.

32:45.700 --> 32:47.440
I've told you many times.

32:47.460 --> 32:49.070
I really have no money.

32:53.950 --> 32:55.080
What a coincidence.

32:55.240 --> 32:58.240
I just received a project bonus of 20,000.

32:56.500 --> 32:59.600
[Minfu Bank Transaction Alert]

32:58.290 --> 32:59.680
And a balance of 6,000.

32:59.700 --> 33:00.790
26,000.

33:01.080 --> 33:02.340
Will that work for you?

33:02.790 --> 33:03.580
Nie Yucheng,

33:04.040 --> 33:05.630
you earn millions a year,

33:05.660 --> 33:06.920
and you give me 26,000?

33:07.290 --> 33:08.750
Are you trying
to brush me off like a beggar?

33:08.750 --> 33:10.380
If you think it's too little,

33:10.410 --> 33:12.010
you can choose not to take it.

33:12.270 --> 33:12.800
Fine.

33:13.400 --> 33:15.440
Then I'll go to the reception, the lobby,

33:15.440 --> 33:16.350
and the hallway,

33:16.350 --> 33:17.550
and ask someone else.

33:19.080 --> 33:20.030
I have no money,

33:20.530 --> 33:21.770
but I have tours.

33:30.550 --> 33:31.550
Our company

33:31.580 --> 33:33.510
has several tours ready to depart.

33:33.730 --> 33:34.930
They're all big ones.

33:34.970 --> 33:36.050
Take your pick.

33:36.510 --> 33:37.640
As for the profit,

33:37.810 --> 33:39.810
you'll get the highest percentage.

33:40.160 --> 33:41.090
Do you want it?

33:48.910 --> 33:52.020
[Changyang Travel Agency Suzhou Tour
Participant Information Sheet]

33:53.660 --> 33:54.420
Yes.

33:55.350 --> 33:56.410
I'll take them all.

33:56.520 --> 33:57.330
Deal.

33:58.010 --> 33:58.820
What?

33:59.160 --> 34:01.380
He just gave you 26,000
and brushed you off?

34:01.380 --> 34:03.980
That Nie guy is so cold-blooded.

34:04.200 --> 34:06.330
I'm going to settle the score with him.

34:07.550 --> 34:08.590
The divorce is already done.

34:08.590 --> 34:10.449
It won't be that easy to get money.

34:10.590 --> 34:11.550
You want to settle the score?

34:11.550 --> 34:13.110
Even if you say
you're his mother-in-law,

34:13.110 --> 34:14.590
he won't acknowledge you.

34:15.880 --> 34:18.440
Miyu served him faithfully for 10 years,

34:18.880 --> 34:20.360
and only got 26,000?

34:21.030 --> 34:22.210
If I had known this would happen,

34:22.210 --> 34:23.810
we should have come earlier.

34:23.880 --> 34:25.550
If we didn't get what we want from him,

34:25.550 --> 34:26.360
we wouldn't have allowed the divorce.

34:26.360 --> 34:28.360
What's the point of saying this now?

34:28.360 --> 34:30.590
What about the 300,000 we still owe?

34:30.590 --> 34:31.440
What can we do?

34:32.880 --> 34:33.670
The son-in-law is gone,

34:33.670 --> 34:35.440
so we go to our daughter.

34:35.800 --> 34:37.860
Let Miyu find a way to cover it for now.

34:37.880 --> 34:39.010
That's all we can do.

34:40.360 --> 34:41.440
Mrs. Nie,

34:41.440 --> 34:43.679
you were a top sales rep at Yuhua before.

34:43.800 --> 34:45.630
I hope you can bring more

34:45.650 --> 34:47.960
honor to our department
after you join Purong.

34:47.960 --> 34:48.510
Mr. Qian,

34:48.510 --> 34:49.670
I will definitely work hard

34:49.670 --> 34:50.960
and not let you down.

34:54.510 --> 34:55.960
You have a meeting later, right?

34:55.960 --> 34:56.960
Please stay.

34:57.110 --> 34:58.610
I'll go to the parking lot by myself.

34:58.610 --> 34:59.180
Alright.

34:59.630 --> 35:00.920
Take care, Mrs. Nie.

35:06.250 --> 35:07.380
Where are you going?

35:07.960 --> 35:08.780
Stop right there.

35:08.780 --> 35:09.780
Stop right there.

35:10.320 --> 35:11.110
Stop!

35:12.070 --> 35:12.880
Stop right there!

35:12.880 --> 35:13.630
Stop!

35:13.880 --> 35:14.880
What are you doing?

35:14.880 --> 35:15.550
You tell me.

35:15.630 --> 35:16.590
You slut!

35:16.590 --> 35:17.360
Homewrecker!

35:17.360 --> 35:20.220
You stole someone's husband
and now you're asking me?

35:20.220 --> 35:21.320
My daughter is good-tempered.

35:21.320 --> 35:22.360
She won't argue with you.

35:22.360 --> 35:22.840
But let me tell you,

35:22.840 --> 35:24.670
as her mother, I'm not done with you.

35:24.670 --> 35:26.360
What nonsense are you talking about?

35:26.360 --> 35:27.670
Be careful. I'll sue you for defamation.

35:27.670 --> 35:28.880
You sue me for defamation?

35:28.880 --> 35:29.470
Fine.

35:29.550 --> 35:30.360
Go ahead and sue me.

35:30.360 --> 35:31.960
Let's make things clear.

35:31.960 --> 35:32.590
Tell me,

35:32.590 --> 35:34.800
didn't you do all those shameless things?

35:34.800 --> 35:35.940
I'm warning you.

35:36.110 --> 35:38.110
It's a fact
that your daughter is divorced.

35:38.110 --> 35:39.920
Don't act like a mother-in-law anymore,

35:39.920 --> 35:40.880
spouting nonsense

35:40.880 --> 35:42.190
and making a scene.

35:42.190 --> 35:42.880
Starting now,

35:42.880 --> 35:44.550
if you say even one more
personal insult to me,

35:44.550 --> 35:45.510
I will sue you.

35:46.440 --> 35:47.880
Sue me then! Sue me!

35:48.360 --> 35:50.070
Stealing someone's husband,
you still have the nerve to sue?

35:50.070 --> 35:52.440
You're making wild accusations
with no evidence.

35:52.440 --> 35:55.000
You two are just desperate
because you can't leech off us anymore.

35:55.000 --> 35:58.360
You freeloaded off my husband
for 10 years and still aren't satisfied.

35:58.360 --> 35:59.150
Shame on you.

35:59.150 --> 35:59.800
Miyu,

35:59.800 --> 36:01.400
it's from the receptionist.

36:02.230 --> 36:03.030
Miyu.

36:03.030 --> 36:03.840
Who-Who...

36:03.840 --> 36:05.320
Security! Security!

36:05.630 --> 36:07.400
Security! Security!

36:08.190 --> 36:10.190
You steal someone's husband and...

36:10.400 --> 36:11.550
What are you doing?

36:16.960 --> 36:17.770
If I were you,

36:17.800 --> 36:18.510
I wouldn't go over there.

36:18.510 --> 36:19.960
They're not your parents.

36:19.960 --> 36:20.860
Calm down.

36:20.960 --> 36:22.000
If you go now,

36:22.000 --> 36:23.000
it will only make things worse.

36:23.000 --> 36:23.800
No matter how bad it gets,

36:23.800 --> 36:25.460
I won't just leave my parents.

36:27.020 --> 36:28.550
Do you know what's going on?

36:28.560 --> 36:29.140
-Let go!
-What?

36:29.140 --> 36:29.910
What?

36:30.920 --> 36:31.230
Seriously.

36:31.230 --> 36:31.670
Sir,

36:31.670 --> 36:33.150
it's a misunderstanding. Sorry.

36:33.150 --> 36:34.320
Please let them go.

36:34.400 --> 36:36.030
Mom, stop making a scene here.

36:36.030 --> 36:37.030
Don't stop me.

36:37.030 --> 36:38.760
I need to settle the score with her.
It's not over.

36:38.760 --> 36:40.540
That's right, Xu Miyu.

36:40.650 --> 36:41.670
Don't be in a rush to leave.

36:41.670 --> 36:43.030
We haven't settled our score yet.

36:43.030 --> 36:44.380
I have nothing to say to you.

36:44.380 --> 36:45.590
Why are you so angry?

36:45.880 --> 36:47.230
We're colleagues now.

36:47.230 --> 36:48.510
We'll be seeing a lot of each other.

36:48.510 --> 36:49.730
Don't make things so tense.

36:49.730 --> 36:50.480
Why colleag-

36:50.600 --> 36:51.630
I still have to thank you

36:51.630 --> 36:53.280
for scheming so hard before

36:53.280 --> 36:54.510
to get me out of Yuhua.

36:54.600 --> 36:55.330
Otherwise,

36:55.360 --> 36:56.880
I wouldn't have gotten a better job.

36:56.880 --> 36:57.510
Right?

36:57.510 --> 36:59.000
Your job lost has nothing to do with me.

36:59.000 --> 37:01.400
I'm not interested in your affairs either.

37:02.510 --> 37:04.440
Drawing a line with me so soon?

37:04.480 --> 37:06.880
Then when you told your dad
to ask my husband for money,

37:06.880 --> 37:08.550
why didn't you draw a clear line?

37:08.550 --> 37:09.160
No, you-

37:09.180 --> 37:09.820
Dad,

37:10.790 --> 37:11.810
what is she talking about?

37:11.810 --> 37:12.880
No, I just wanted to...

37:12.880 --> 37:14.550
Still playing innocent?

37:14.550 --> 37:15.500
You guys

37:15.520 --> 37:17.920
snatched 6 deals all at once
from my husband.

37:17.920 --> 37:19.360
Even the little bonus he just got

37:19.360 --> 37:21.150
was all taken by you.

37:21.230 --> 37:24.510
You're really robbing
under the guise of begging.

37:25.230 --> 37:27.000
Xu Miyu, I'm impressed.

37:27.140 --> 37:29.540
On the surface,
you act so pure and refined,

37:29.670 --> 37:32.190
but turn around and have your parents
ask your ex-husband for money.

37:32.190 --> 37:34.390
You really want everything, don't you?

37:34.440 --> 37:34.960
Dad,

37:35.920 --> 37:37.380
did you go see Nie Yucheng?

37:37.550 --> 37:39.150
Didn't I tell you not to look for him?

37:39.150 --> 37:40.840
I have nothing to do with him now.

37:40.840 --> 37:41.840
Aren't you making

37:42.230 --> 37:43.440
a fool of yourself going to him now?

37:43.440 --> 37:44.710
I just wanted to help you.

37:44.710 --> 37:45.670
You really...

37:45.670 --> 37:47.420
How can you have no conscience?

37:47.510 --> 37:48.360
It was Nie Yucheng

37:48.360 --> 37:48.880
who cheated on you

37:48.880 --> 37:50.400
and let our whole family down.

37:50.400 --> 37:52.240
Your dad went to get justice for you.

37:52.240 --> 37:53.400
How could you scold him?

37:53.400 --> 37:54.670
And her. She...

37:54.670 --> 37:56.190
She stole your man.

37:56.190 --> 37:57.800
You don't blame her but blame us instead.

37:57.800 --> 37:58.880
You really have no conscience. You...

37:58.880 --> 38:00.360
Mom, I didn't mean it that way.

38:00.360 --> 38:01.070
What do you mean?

38:01.070 --> 38:02.030
You're taking an outsider's side.

38:02.030 --> 38:02.880
We're helping you.

38:02.880 --> 38:03.630
Come here.

38:03.630 --> 38:04.920
It's shot more clearly here.

38:04.920 --> 38:05.880
We're helping you.

38:05.880 --> 38:07.210
Alright, stop talking.

38:08.710 --> 38:09.710
You blame me, huh?

38:11.090 --> 38:11.860
Fine.

38:13.030 --> 38:14.030
I'll just pretend

38:14.360 --> 38:16.560
I never raised you as my daughter, okay?

38:16.560 --> 38:17.600
Let's go!

38:17.800 --> 38:18.630
Hey, don't...

38:19.880 --> 38:20.400
Wait for me!

38:20.400 --> 38:21.190
Dad! Mom!

38:21.190 --> 38:23.510
What a family of drama queens.

38:23.920 --> 38:25.880
I should set up a stage for you.

38:27.710 --> 38:29.230
Lu Zhenzhen, I'm warning you.

38:29.230 --> 38:30.840
Stop staring at other people's lives.

38:30.840 --> 38:32.170
Mind your own business.

38:36.550 --> 38:37.880
Dad, Mom!

38:38.760 --> 38:39.480
Mom!

38:40.230 --> 38:40.890
Dad!

38:42.960 --> 38:44.230
Don't call me Dad.

38:44.480 --> 38:45.920
Deep down,

38:45.920 --> 38:48.150
you never really treated me like your dad.

38:48.150 --> 38:49.320
It's not like that.

38:49.370 --> 38:50.730
Then what is it like?

38:50.760 --> 38:52.840
Just now, in front of so many people,

38:52.860 --> 38:55.090
you made me lose so much face.

38:55.250 --> 38:57.020
I'm at this age.

38:57.190 --> 38:58.690
It's bad enough I can't enjoy a good life,

38:58.690 --> 38:59.510
but I also have to

38:59.510 --> 39:01.760
make a fool of myself in public for you.

39:02.190 --> 39:02.880
And you,

39:03.070 --> 39:04.510
you never call,

39:04.510 --> 39:05.690
but when you do,

39:05.710 --> 39:07.150
you just ask for money.

39:07.440 --> 39:10.480
How did it become my fault?

39:11.230 --> 39:11.800
For all these years,

39:11.800 --> 39:13.920
I haven't asked the family
for a single penny.

39:13.920 --> 39:16.510
I've always tried my best to help out
when the family was in trouble.

39:16.510 --> 39:18.000
You said you wanted to open a guesthouse,

39:18.000 --> 39:18.920
and you didn't have enough money,

39:18.920 --> 39:20.360
so you needed
to take out a loan in my name.

39:20.360 --> 39:21.060
No problem.

39:21.190 --> 39:22.400
I'll take out the loan.

39:22.400 --> 39:23.820
The guesthouse just opened,

39:23.820 --> 39:24.960
and business wasn't good,

39:24.960 --> 39:26.480
so I've been helping to pay off the loan.

39:26.480 --> 39:28.000
You both know that.

39:28.020 --> 39:29.690
What do you mean by this?

39:29.960 --> 39:31.590
Are you trying
to settle scores with me now?

39:31.590 --> 39:32.200
Fine.

39:32.230 --> 39:33.670
Let's get things straight.

39:33.670 --> 39:35.630
Although I'm not your biological father,

39:35.630 --> 39:37.790
you've been in this family
since you were little.

39:37.790 --> 39:39.440
I provided you with food and clothes,

39:39.440 --> 39:40.360
and paid for your college.

39:40.360 --> 39:40.880
Right?

39:41.070 --> 39:43.070
So is it wrong for you to help out

39:43.070 --> 39:43.840
the family now?

39:43.840 --> 39:46.230
We're not asking you for a fortune.

39:46.550 --> 39:48.480
You finally married a good man.

39:48.670 --> 39:50.360
But look at what you've done

39:50.360 --> 39:52.000
to this family.

39:53.440 --> 39:54.320
You did

39:54.320 --> 39:56.360
choose a life that made you happy.

39:56.880 --> 39:58.670
But when you chose this life,

39:58.670 --> 39:59.880
did you ever consider

39:59.880 --> 40:02.320
the family that raised you?

40:03.200 --> 40:04.060
And you even...

40:07.540 --> 40:09.740
How much you've spoiled your daughter!

40:13.190 --> 40:14.360
He's your stepfather,

40:14.360 --> 40:16.030
but I'm your biological mother.

40:16.030 --> 40:17.800
It's not easy for us to live

40:17.800 --> 40:19.510
under other's roof.

40:20.400 --> 40:21.550
I've told you since you were little

40:21.550 --> 40:22.760
to be caring

40:22.760 --> 40:24.070
and grateful.

40:24.480 --> 40:26.190
Why don't you understand?

40:27.030 --> 40:27.920
I'm telling you,

40:27.920 --> 40:29.400
you need to get it straight.

40:29.400 --> 40:30.630
Don't ask your dad

40:30.630 --> 40:32.630
for 5,000 yuan every month anymore.

40:33.340 --> 40:34.130
Mom,

40:35.320 --> 40:36.710
that 5,000 yuan...

40:37.800 --> 40:38.510
I didn't

40:38.510 --> 40:40.710
borrow the money for myself.

40:40.710 --> 40:42.320
Why are you still dawdling?

40:42.680 --> 40:43.320
Yourself.

40:43.320 --> 40:43.710
Yourself.

40:43.710 --> 40:44.360
All

40:44.360 --> 40:45.590
you know is yourself.

40:45.620 --> 40:46.920
You had the guts to get a divorce.

40:46.920 --> 40:48.750
Why don't you have the guts to make money?

40:48.750 --> 40:49.710
Coming!

40:50.600 --> 40:51.320
Jeez.
